1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
We are establishing a task force for the Kira case.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,500
The Commissioner General has issued orders to treat this case as the highest priority.

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Those who participate in the investigation must be prepared to risk their lives.

4
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,500
According to L's analysis, Kira resides in the Kanto region
and is most likely a student or a working professional.

5
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
There is a pattern in the times of death of the criminals.
On weekdays, deaths occur after the evening. On weekends, they are irregular.

6
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:46,500
In other words, Kira has other activities during the day.
Most likely school or work.

7
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
Analysis of the killing method is also progressing.
Kira requires both a name and a face.

8
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,500
Since only criminals who have been covered by the media have died,
it is believed that Kira obtains information through media sources.

9
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
The personal information of investigators must be strictly managed.
If our names are leaked, we too could become targets.

10
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,500
A message from L: "Anyone who may come into contact with Kira
must never reveal their real name."

11
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,000
Father, are you involved in the Kira investigation?

12
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:31,500
Light, I cannot tell you anything about this matter.
It is for our family's safety.

13
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,000
I understand. I believe that you are doing the right thing, Father.

14
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:46,500
The further the investigation progresses, the closer they get to me.
But this is within my expectations.

15
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
The fact that my father is in the Kira task force
means I can keep track of the investigation's progress.

16
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:01,500
I will acknowledge L's deductive abilities.
But without evidence, he cannot catch me.

17
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:09,000
As long as no one knows this notebook exists,
it is impossible to uncover Kira's true identity.

18
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:16,500
Continue your investigation, L.
The closer you get, the deeper you fall into my trap.

19
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Everything is going according to plan.

20
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:31,000
In this battle of wits, I will be the one who laughs last.
